These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, dubstep, rock, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, japanese, british, colombian
There 4 different types of food: orange, corn, avocado, peach
1. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left of the british##1
4. the fan of gospel is the canadian##1
5. the canadian is on the right of the british##1
6. the person eating orange is on the left of the colombian##1
7. the japanese is on the left of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre    | dubstep  | pop | rock    | gospel       |
| Nationality         | japanese | colombian    | british      | canadian |
| Food   | orange   | avocado | corn | peach        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, bellflower, sunflower, orchid
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, action, fantasy, animation
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, disco, gospel, r&b
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
5. the fan of indie is the person watching spy movies##1
6. the fan of r&b is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Flower        | sunflower   | bellflower | amaryllis     | orchid      |
| Movie-Genre         | action | fantasy | animation | spy |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | r&b   | gospel     | indie      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, trike
City: liverpool, venice, london, colone
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, biathlon, rowing, sailing
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the trike is the person traveling to london##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the person driving the bus is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Transport         | bus | motorbike | quad-bike | trike |
| City   | colone       | venice    | liverpool | london     |
| Sport   | weightlifting | rowing    | sailing | biathlon    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, chaman, alhambra, vegafina
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, hip-hop, r&b, electronic
4 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, chess, bridge
1. the alhambra-smoker is the person playing bridge##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
6. the fan of trance is the alhambra-smoker##1
7. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
8. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Cigar         | montecristo | vegafina | alhambra | chaman |
| Music-Genre       | hip-hop     | electronic      | trance     | r&b      |
| Game   | backgammon | canasta         | bridge      | chess        |

