.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, ivory, red, yellow
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, mouse, rabbit, bird
1. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who likes red##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person drinking fanta is the person who likes ivory##1
7. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage         | mirinda   | sprite | coffee  | fanta      |
| Color   | red  | pink        | yellow  | ivory       |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | rabbit    | mouse | bird |

