.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
House: farmhouse, wooden, victorian, tower
There 4 different types of food: pepper, cranberry, grapefruit, cabbage
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, ritmeester, oliveros, dunhill
1. the farmhouse house is the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the right of the tower house##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the wooden house is on the far left##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is the victorian house##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
8. the tower house is the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| House           | wooden | victorian | tower | farmhouse |
| Food   | cabbage   | grapefruit  | cranberry | pepper   |
| Cigar   | dunhill   | alhambra     | oliveros | ritmeester       |

