.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, brazilian, indonesian, italian
4 different games are played: chess, backgammon, bridge, monopoly
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, fisherman, nurse
1. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
2. the brazilian is on the far right##1
3. the designer is on the left of the librarian##1
4. the librarian is the indonesian##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the canadian##1
6. the fisherman is on the left of the designer##1
7. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
8. the person playing backgammon is the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Nationality          | canadian  | italian | indonesian   | brazilian     |
| Game         | monopoly | backgammon   | chess  | bridge |
| Job   | fisherman         | designer  | librarian | nurse  |

