.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
House: craftsman, futuristic, victorian, ranch-style
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, fishing, sudoku, video-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, jet-ski, tram, train
1. the futuristic house is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person driving the train is the victorian house##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the train##1
8. the futuristic house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| House      | ranch-style | victorian     | craftsman | futuristic |
| Hobby   | video-games  | hiking | sudoku       | fishing    |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | train | ship    | tram |

