.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, nigerian, french, russian
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, lilac, blood-red, light-blue
City: san-francisco, new-york, liverpool, rome
1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the russian##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is the nigerian##1
5. the nigerian is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the french##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality          | french        | russian   | nigerian  | dutch   |
| Color   | aquamarine         | light-blue     | lilac    | blood-red       |
| City         | new-york | san-francisco | liverpool | rome |

