.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, writing, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, soul, r&b, gospel
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, spy, musical, scientific
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the fan of soul##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | writing    | skydiving | woodworking | filmmaking        |
| Music-Genre       | gospel | funk  | soul | r&b     |
| Movie-Genre        | spy    | musical   | scientific  | epic |

