.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, dubstep, trance, classical
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, soy-milk, fanta
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bolivar, cain, dannemann
1. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is the cain-smoker##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Music-Genre         | reggae  | classical | dubstep  | trance |
| Beverage       | soy-milk | mirinda        | fanta | iced-tea       |
| Cigar   | swisher   | bolivar          | dannemann          | cain       |

