.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald, grey, aquamarine
There 4 different types of food: onion, pineapple, watermelon, pear
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, soccer, badminton
1. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person eating onion##1
2. the person eating pear is the person who likes emerald##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
5. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the person who likes ivory is the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color         | aquamarine   | grey   | ivory | emerald |
| Food   | watermelon | onion | pineapple   | pear |
| Sport   | badminton     | sailing  | soccer  | rugby  |

