3. the italian is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
7. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Nationality         | thai | argentine    | american        | italian |
| Game   | bridge     | go     | billiard        | snooker   |
| Flower         | marigold   | aconite | begonia | iris  |

