4. the indian is on the right of the australian##1
5. the person who growszinnia is the person eating raspberry##1
6. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the mexican##1
7. the person eating cabbage is the person who growsdaisy##1
8. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Food      | cabbage        | raspberry    | cranberry | corn      |
| Flower   | daisy        | zinnia   | bellflower  | poppy  |
| Nationality         | australian | indian | mexican   | nigerian |

