4. the person who likes green is the person playing domino##1
5. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is the person who likes ivory##1
7. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
