.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, june, january, february
4 different games are played: chess, domino, poker, snooker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, mirinda, almond-milk
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
4. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
5. the person playing chess is the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
8. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Birthday           | june  | january  | october | february |
| Game   | snooker   | chess | domino   | poker      |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | mirinda    | hot-chocolate   | almond-milk         |

 